high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the salt shaker behind the pepper mill on the counter.
Turn left and look down at the cabinet below the counter.
Open the cabinet door, place the salt shaker in the cabinet, close the door.
Walk up to the counter.
Pick up the salt shaker on the right.
Look down at the cabinet below the counter.
Open the door, place the salt shaker inside the cabinet, close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two salt shakers to the cabinet below the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room then look up.
Take one of the salt shakers to the left of the stove.
Turn to the right and take one step, then turn to the left to face the stove, then turn left and look down.
Open the cabinet directly ahead and put the salt shaker in the cabinet then close the door.
Look up at the counter.
Take the salt shaker on the right side of the counter.
Turn around and take one step, then turn around and face the counter and look down.
Open the cabinet directly ahead and put the salt shaker in the cabinet then close the door.
Turn to your right and go to the corner counter top, to the left of the stove.
Pick up the salt grinder from the counter to the left of the stove
Step back from the stove and turn to your left.
Place the salt grinder in the bottom cabinet, around the left corner of the stove.
Step back away from the cabinet.
Pick up the pepper grinder from the corner counter to the left of the stove.
Move back from the counter again.
Place the pepper grinder in the cabinet around the left corner, after the stove, to the left of the salt grinder.
anns.task_desc: Put the salt and pepper grinders in the cabinet.
